WAR TAB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
United Nations approval or not, the United States should not be allowed to go 
to war until we can pay for the conflict in cash. 
</P>
<P>
VICTOR PETERSON, Oxnard 
</P>
