STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EGYPT; SADAT, ANWAR; HUSSEIN, SADDAM; IRAQ -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; MILITARY 
CONFRONTATIONS 
</P>
